{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·009.1", "text_original": "有女同車，顏如舜華，將翱將翔，佩玉瓊琚，彼美孟姜，洵美且都。", "text_normalized": "有女同車，顏如舜華，將翱將翔，佩玉瓊琚，彼美孟姜，洵美且都。", "notes": "有女同車 Chinese stanza 1."}
